{"tid":805791,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"CNN：香港科學家(s)發明新‘納米swarm‘ robots","createTime":"2018-09-04T06:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T09:33:57.000Z","uid":165773,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5f912803c739c43596b88eb1ff44ff6db7eb0e55","tid":805791,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T06:30:39.000Z","msg":"2018年9月4日 CNN(health)<br />\n<br />\n香港中文大學曾教授，帶領研究團隊發明左具有突破性意義既ribbon形狀納米robots。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/142220_0e1f3c7452fa4dea09a753c6d4485a46.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F142220_0e1f3c7452fa4dea09a753c6d4485a46.gif&h=98852531&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n賣點係可以透過磁場震動，準確控制大量每個只得5份1紅血球size既robot仔，高速地做出精準同複雜變化既群體移動：包括擴散、收縮、裂隊、聚合。其行動速度同效率係有史以來最高。<br />\n<br />\n更重要係佢地可以游走在人類、動物體內通過狹窄血管、打穿血管閉塞血塊、運用藥物直達器官。<br />\n<br />\n曾教授同緊威爾斯親王醫院合作，相信五年內可以應用於手術上，特別係胃、腸疾病。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/141756_dddd2061870ea596355d5708d5920783.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F141756_dddd2061870ea596355d5708d5920783.png&h=454831ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾教授話，研究目標之一係學大自然既雀仔、魚、昆蟲、細菌都有swarm既行為，利用集群智能(swarm intelligence) 高效率地解決各種個體解決唔倒既問題。<br />\n<br />\n佢表示，研究靈感部分來自電影Big Hero Six、Transformers。劇中有大量小型機械人集體行動。<br />\n<br />\n目前該robots應用仍有局限，例如心臟血液速度太快會被一野衝走。<br />\n<br />\n曾教授表示「希望多D人關注納米robots研究，好刺激。」<br />\n<br />\n「我成日同學生講，大家一齊做研究就好似一場冒險，唔知前面會有咩發現。」"},{"pid":"a23a7d9d1f878dd2dcf07041e400cfb71ad6d765","tid":805791,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T06:31:48.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong scientists develop new 'nano-swarm' robots<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/2018/09/04/health/nano-swarm-robots-intl/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2Fhealth%2Fnano-swarm-robots-intl%2F&d=AE7adLJ16%2Bv8t4P6ZbmGqozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=afc62f0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2Fhealth%2Fnano-swarm-robots-intl%2F&h=6e31c419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnn.com/2018/09/04/health/nano-swarm-robots-intl/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41467-018-05749-6#Sec12\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41467-018-05749-6%23Sec12&d=AE7adLJ16%2Bv8t4P6ZbmGqozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=2f550384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41467-018-05749-6#Sec12</a>"},{"pid":"a2ac6572bd469b9006aed398e92fc5f5a2aaf4d7","tid":805791,"uid":15813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T06:36:38.000Z","msg":"係咪即係有望減低通波仔手術既風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89a8ce70fd72359347886358022d661dbbbfb62","tid":805791,"uid":165773,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a2ac6572bd469b9006aed398e92fc5f5a2aaf4d7","tid":805791,"uid":15813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T06:36:38.000Z","msg":"係咪即係有望減低通波仔手術既風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T06:39:12.000Z","msg":"照篇文講就係 可以叫堆robot仔一野衝爆個D血塊s"},{"pid":"a454c374c22c5f767118db288e0db66eb862f091","tid":805791,"uid":15813,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d89a8ce70fd72359347886358022d661dbbbfb62","tid":805791,"uid":165773,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a2ac6572bd469b9006aed398e92fc5f5a2aaf4d7","tid":805791,"uid":15813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T06:36:38.000Z","msg":"係咪即係有望減低通波仔手術既風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T06:39:12.000Z","msg":"照篇文講就係 可以叫堆robot仔一野衝爆個D血塊s"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T06:40:36.000Z","msg":"咁睇黎中風都有得救wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e6e586755ab88863191f5811b75b0df4fd68f34","tid":805791,"uid":34058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T06:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1033d8d063803014db33ae9ea5ec3e7e83462ef5","tid":805791,"uid":122264,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T08:01:42.000Z","msg":"係病人條血管寫個屌字"},{"pid":"7a73ae9a0d72016fc02fb5716bb5fed934b0aba3","tid":805791,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T08:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e890ad8af8fe21ea9af29e69f71b2ed898e8553c","tid":805791,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T08:19:03.000Z","msg":"中學嗰陣睇節目話<br />\n要送人上火星就要喺太空人身體入面放啲納米機械人去不斷殺細菌<br />\n等佢喺成大半年嘅旅程入面都唔會病 <br />\n嗰陣時仲覺得係天方夜譚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n而家連火星都要有排先去到<br />\n納米機械人已經俾人發明咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc93407b529a00e677fb7924afde3a6b4cd8b8b","tid":805791,"uid":162820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:33:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/173340_ec265176bf7362a19b92818cb23b2547.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F173340_ec265176bf7362a19b92818cb23b2547.gif&h=ffed6576&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}